headline: Chubb Appoints Brian Church to Lead International Property and Casualty Division
summary: Chubb today announced that Brian Church has been appointed Division President, Property and Casualty, for Chubb Overseas General Insurance (COG), the company's international general insurance operations, effective immediately.
